data.description: Welcome to Dinner Lake Shores in beautiful Lake Wales, Florida. This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom homes is move in ready! This home has been well kept and very clean. Gated community just minutes from shopping and major highways. Centrally located between Orlando and Tampa. You will love the updated kitchen granite counters and beautiful backsplash recently installed. With a relaxing patio you can enjoy the Florida breeze or sit in the Florida sunshine on the back yard deck. There is a retractable awning for more coverage over the deck if desired. Pavers installed on back patio and front walkway. The large family room accompanied with high ceilings is a great space for gatherings. This neighborhood is very quiet and gated. The front room could be used as a 4th bedroom if needed. Call for a showing appointment!
